		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">MatthewCallis wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">What would be the point of this switch if it toggles the name table mirroring? I guess I don't understand why they would need to change the name table mirroring externally.</div>
<br />Perhaps to use different games on the same developer board. Imagine a studio working on two titles that use different mirroring, where one title's team gets to test on RealHardware(tm) in the morning and the other in the afternoon.

		

