		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well I don't remember this game to scroll. Acroding to bootgod, it uses vertical mirroring, while the other NROM game developped by the same company used horizontal mirroring (Door Door), but the game came out significantly earler. The other game being under developpement at the same time uses vertical mirroring as well and is CNROM (Dragon Quest), I don't know if it could have been tested on that board.

		

