		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well, the fact that the game does not scroll has nothing to do with the board having a mirroring switch... in fact, if the game doesn't scroll, that must be exactly why the poster hasn't noticed anything. Anyway, if a company has a devcart with a mirroring switch, they'll test their games with it whether they scroll or not.

		

